Package stacks

Class StackList<T>

java.lang.Object
stacks.StackList<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class StackList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>
A parameterized class which implements Iterable. StackList is a singly linked list / stack used to store internet URLs as Strings. StackList has 2 inner classes StackIterator and Node, which are used in structuring the data passed to StackList.
